description: This is the entry point for a React application, responsible for rendering the root component ('App') into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports React libraries, styles, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to manage React DOM rendering for a specific DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the DOM managed by the root.
